## 🎯 Quick Start

### For First Time Setup:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/relationship-adviser.git
cd relationship-adviser
bun install
bun run db:push
cp .env.example .env.local
bun run dev
```

### For Demo Preparation:
1. Read `DEMO-GUIDE.md`
2. Review `QUICK-REFERENCE.md`
3. Practice with `test@example.com` / `password123`

### For GitHub Setup:
1. Read `GITHUB-SETUP.md`
2. Run `./setup-github.sh`
3. Create repo on GitHub
4. Push with `git push origin main`

