## 🔐 Security Summary

### Implemented:
- ✅ bcrypt password hashing (10 rounds)
- ✅ JWT tokens (7 days expiry)
- ✅ Protected API routes
- ✅ Input validation
- ✅ SQL injection prevention
- ✅ .gitignore for sensitive files

### Not in Git:
- ❌ .env (contains JWT_SECRET)
- ❌ .env.local
- ❌ db/*.db (database files)
- ❌ node_modules/

